                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Dans l'orage, et, pensif, on dit aux quatre.vents",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "De la porter à Dieu par dessus les vivants.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Et l'on s'arrête, et puis on attend. Toujours l'onde.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
